title: Pedestrian pushing shopping cart hit, killed on I-80 in Vallejo
text:
Photo: Google Maps A pedestrian was struck and killed when he walked into the path of a vehicle on Interstate 80 near Tennessee Street in Vallejo on Tuesday night. A pedestrian was struck and killed when he walked into the path of...
A man pushing a shopping cart against traffic in the fast lane on Interstate 80 was struck by a car and killed Tuesday night in Vallejo, California Highway Patrol officials said.
